            <l n="d">stambhārambhāya śambhavē</l>
        </lg>
     <p>namo rājagurave ||</p> <!--not in the printed edition!-->
  
<ab>{spiral}</ab>
   <p xml:lang="kan-Latn">
<lb n="3"/>svasti samasta-bhuvanāśraya śrī-pṛthvī-vallabha mahārājādhirāja paramēśvara parama-bhaṭṭā-
raka kāḷaṁjara-pu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ra-varādhīśvara suvarṇṇa-vṛṣabha-dhvaja ḍamaruka-tūryya-nirghōṣaṇu <!-- correct to: nirghoṣaṇa --> kaḷa-
